summary:
Looking for a position as: application manager, - supporter, - developer 
or Linux, database, network administrator

Expertise: Unix/Linux, Databases, Programming and Networks

Soft Skills: Client oriented, Good communication skills both verbally and written, Analytical, Punctual, Self motivated, Team-player

Tech Skills:
Database related (15 years)
Oracle, PL/SQL, dBaseIV, MySQL, data modelling, functional and technical application management and data migration

Unix/Linux and network related (5 years)
Compile, install and configure, Shell script, Squid, Squidguard, Postfix, Spamassassin, Freeradius, LTSP, Samba, X-windows, Apache, WAN, fibre optical networks, wireless networks, LAN, TCP/IP, SMTP, DNS, POP3, HTTP, VOIP, (Cisco) routers, DHCP, SSL

Other
Pascal, C, Perl, PHP, Windows server 2000/2003, Terminal Server & Thin Clients, Clipper, XML, Javascript, HTML, CSS
